window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Captain Jason Burke and his crew are used to danger, but nothing prepares them for the terror stalking the stars.</p> <p>A savage killer, born from twisted science and driven by vengeance, leaves a trail of butchered victims across remote worlds.</p> <p>When Omega Force is drawn into the hunt, they uncover a secret that threatens not just their lives but the lives of thousands of innocents. With a predator who knows no mercy, Jason must confront his past and a truth that could destroy everything he’s fought for. In a galaxy where trust is a luxury, can Omega Force outrun the hunter—or will they become the hunted?</p>"; 
